    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 * (wp.sin(v0 + 0.94) / (v2 + 0.22 + v2 + 0.71)))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.30)
    v2 = ((v0 / (v1 + 0.97 * tmp + 0.16)) * ((v1 + 0.58 - v2 + 0.77) * 0.37))
    v2 = 0.74
    tmp = (tmp / ((v1 + 0.91 + v0 + 0.06) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.26)))
    data[tid] = v0
